 href=\"https://i.v2ex.co/Hn4w3Vdv.jpeg\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://i.v2ex.co/Hn4w3Vdv.jpeg</a></p>\n", "last_modified": 1645331839, "replies": 41, "id": 835177}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc49/0ca4/65_large.png?m=1524891806", "name": "google", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc49/0ca4/65_normal.png?m=1524891806", "title": "Google", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/google", "topics": 2759, "footer": "", "header": "Google’s mission is to organize the world’s information and make it universally accessible and useful.", "title_alternative": "Google", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc49/0ca4/65_mini.png?m=1524891806", "stars": 3336, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 65, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"id": 455199, "username": "teliang", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/teliang", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "马来西亚", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cd15/3421/455199_mini.png?m=1645348421", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cd15/3421/455199_normal.png?m=1645348421", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cd15/3421/455199_large.png?m=1645348421", "created": 1574626564, "last_modified": 1645348421}, "last_reply_by": "teliang", "last_touched": 1645411747, "title": "救命， Google 存储空间不足，想购买存储空间但是无法绑定信用卡", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/835220", "created": 1645349623, "deleted": 0, "content": "如题，我有一张浦发 VISA 的双币卡（可以正常使用的），但是购买 Google One 方案绑定信用卡的时候，提示\r\n\r\n\r\n**您的发卡机构拒绝了此请求。请与您的银行联系，或使用其他付款方式。详细了解 [OR-CCSEH-26]**\r\n\r\n\r\n然后我打电话问浦发的客服，她说是因为 Google 商家的信用评级太低交易无法支付，叫我改用别的方式支付。言外之意我是懂的，所以想问一下大家现在都用什么方式支付的。", "content_rendered": "<p>如题，我有一张浦发 VISA 的双币卡（可以正常使用的），但是购买 Google One 方案绑定信用卡的时候，提示</p>\n<p><strong>您的发卡机构拒绝了此请求。请与您的银行联系，或使用其他付款方式。详细了解 [OR-CCSEH-26]</strong></p>\n<p>然后我打电话问浦发的客服，她说是因为 Google 商家的信用评级太低交易无法支付，叫我改用别的方式支付。言外之意我是懂的，所以想问一下大家现在都用什么方式支付的。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1645350162, "replies": 40, "id